the horn and also
मुरलीं नितम्बके
the flute, in the waist band
निवेशयन्
tucking
कबलधर: कराम्बुजे
a ball of rice holding in the lotus like hand
प्रहासयन्
making (them) laugh
कलवचनै:
by humorous talks
कुमारकान् बुभोजिथ
the boys, (Thou) ate
त्रिदशगणै:
by the gods
मुदा नुत:
